name: The Prisoner - No Faith  Chairit Prapai

metadata.name: The Prisoner 01
metadata.description:
When we can't let all our emotions out and show it to anyone. We are like a prisoner.

This project wants to show the human emotions that are suppressed within through fashion photography.

When sometimes, we are unable to release our own emotions to the people around us to know. 

It is like a prisoner who is imprisoned without freedom.

Original photography: Chairit Prapai
Photo manipulation: No Faith / Federico Salvador
